Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:27.16,Eden,Akira,0,0,0,,{Hello.}Xin chào.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.16,0:15:29.45,Eden,Akira,0,0,0,,{Pants-kun, are you around?}Pantsu-kun, có nhà không?
