Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.96,Eden,Micchon,0,0,0,,{You need to flatter him.}Lý ra phải tâng bốc anh ta kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:45.09,Eden,Akira,0,0,0,,{Then Mittan, you call him.}Vậy Mittan gọi cậu ta đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:46.88,Eden,Itazu,0,0,0,,{It's god damn noisy.}Gì mà ồn dữ vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:49.18,Eden,Itazu,0,0,0,,{Who the heck is yakking away in front of someone's home?}Ai lại đi cãi vả trước cửa nhà người ta thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:52.85,Eden,Itazu,0,0,0,,{Oh? Micchon, you're here?}Ồ? Micchon đến đấy hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:58.27,Eden,Akira,0,0,0,,{Oh, you're Pants-kun?}Ô, cậu là Pantsu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:00.48,Eden,Itazu,0,0,0,,{I've no interest in you!}Tôi không quen biết anh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:03.73,Eden,Itazu,0,0,0,,{The lady from the bakery is here too?}Cô nương tiệm bánh cũng có mặt hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:06.70,Eden,Saki,0,0,0,,{Yeah. It's been a while. How have you been?}Vâng. Lâu rồi không gặp, cậu thế nào rồi?
