Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.11,0:16:44.61,Eden,Micchon,0,0,0,,{What are you up to?}Thiệt là...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:45.90,Eden,Akira,0,0,0,,{Oh well.}Thôi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.32,Eden,Akira,0,0,0,,{Just get him those magazines.}Cứ mua giúp cậu ta đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:48.86,Eden,Saki,0,0,0,,{Let's go, Micchon.}Đi thôi, Micchon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.25,Eden,Itazu,0,0,0,,{I won't meet you even if you do that.}Đừng tưởng làm thế thì tôi sẽ tiếp anh nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.21,Eden,Akira,0,0,0,,{Hey, Itazu.}Nè, Itazu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:08.26,Eden,Akira,0,0,0,,{Are you interested in things to do with Seleção?}Cậu quan tâm những chuyện liên quan Seleção thì phải?
