Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.48,0:18:09.19,Eden,Micchon,0,0,0,,{It's not as if he really shut himself in his room because he lost his trousers... I think.}Anh ta trốn trong phòng không hẳn\Nchỉ vì bị mất cái quần... Em nghĩ vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:11.95,Eden,Saki,0,0,0,,{I see.}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:16.87,Eden,Itazu,0,0,0,,{It's true...}Đúng là thật...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:18.91,Eden,Itazu,0,0,0,,{He's saying “Say mercy.”}Anh ta bảo “Nói gyafun”.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:20.12,Eden,Akira,0,0,0,,{See?}Thấy chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:22.50,Eden,Itazu,0,0,0,,{When did you notice that?}Anh phát hiện ra khi nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:24.46,Eden,Akira,0,0,0,,{I was the one that made him do it.}Tôi chính là người ra lệnh mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:30.38,Eden,Akira,0,0,0,,{Be it the incident about the twenty thousand missing NEETs which people confused with the Johnny Hunter,}Và sự kiện liên quan hai vạn NEET mất tích mà người ta nhầm lẫn với Tay săn Johnny,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:32.17,Eden,Akira,0,0,0,,{and yesterday's incident at Roppongi,}lẫn sự kiện ở Roppongi hôm nọ,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:35.47,Eden,Akira,0,0,0,,{or even how they are all tied to the Seleção,}hay bất kể chuyện gì có dính líu tới Seleção,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:37.60,Eden,Akira,0,0,0,,{I can probably tell you quite a lot about them.}tôi đều có thể kể cho cậu nghe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:44.60,Eden,Itazu,0,0,0,,{Thinking that the Johnny Hunter and NEET incidents were the same was a common theory on the Internet.}Lẫn lộn chuyện Tay săn Johnny với vụ NEET là ý kiến chung trên Net.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:47.31,Eden,Itazu,0,0,0,,{Who are you?}Anh là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:50.36,Eden,Akira,0,0,0,,{I've already told you that I'm a Seleção.}Tôi đã bảo mình là Seleção.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:53.90,Eden,Akira,0,0,0,,{Open up, Itazu.}Mở ra đi, Itazu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:59.37,Eden,Akira,0,0,0,,{You should believe me after you analyze this phone.}Cậu sẽ tin tôi sau khi phân tích chiếc điện thoại này.
